column1: #Text=Anime North convention brings fans to Toronto
#Text=last weekend , North American anime and manga convention Anime North was held .
#Text=Anime North sprawled across multiple venues , including the Toronto Congress Centre , as a fan-run celebration of Japanese pop culture .
#Text=Wikinews 's Nicholas Moreau was in attendance to photograph the event .
#Text=Carmen Cosplay as Snow White , Aileen Cosplay as Rapunzel , and Grey Dickson as Flynn .
#Text=Binrand Cosplay as Shyvana from League of Legends .
#Text=Montrealer " Aileen Cosplay " was wearing an outfit of Rapunzel from the Disney animated film Tangled , when Wikinews photographed her .
#Text=Wikinews talked with her after the event , learning that she was one of the " Estrada Sisters " , who have been dressing up as pop culture characters for roughly a decade .
